The <b>Vinje Hotel</b> was built in 1876, and was one of the first hotels in the Swiss and dragon style.  It currently (2010) has 46 rooms and features a &quot;large beautiful traditional Norwegian dining room&quot;.  There also are 10 cabins on the property. [<a href="http://www.vinjeturisthotel.no" rel="nofollow">1</a>] [<a href="http://www.fotovoss.com/vinje_hotel.htm" rel="nofollow">2</a>] 

